data.description: This is a great South Suburb home with LOTS of updates! The kitchen is all redone with new cabinets, countertops and appliances! Bathroom is all nicely updated and fresh also. New floors throughout most of the home along with fresh paint. There is a 2 car garage PLUS and nice sized shop in the back with alley access. This one has it all! The bonus room/extra family room is really the only thing left, so make it what and how you would like!
